<div>
  GSD adds an <code>aiPrReviewer</code> Pipeline step for AI-assisted pull request review (GitHub + Anthropic),
  in the spirit of the <a href="https://subzone.github.io/ad-ai-pr-reviewer/">AI PR Reviewer</a> Azure DevOps extension.
  See <a href="https://www.jenkins.io/doc/developer/publishing/requesting-hosting/">Update Center hosting</a> for publication.
</div>
